{
  "stem": "6736.1",
  "chunk_idx": 5,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.8,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And it was-- the commotion was that the whole shul could hear, the argument back and forth.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And finally, the elderly people won the-- the argument, because they said, we have a big God, ein grosser Gott.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And God will help us.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "The believing in God was so strong that we felt we are protected by God.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 6 SECONDS]",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yiddish and-- and Polish.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Of course, there was-- there was no question about it.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "It was written up, uh, in Europe some terrible things.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But again, [PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] nobody was prepared.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "First, they said, he's not going to touch Poland.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "If he's going to touch Poland, France and England and America, they are going to declare war against the Germans.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And Hitler will not be that crazy to start fighting with the whole world.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So there was, ah-- I see it now, it was wishful thinking.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But on the other hand, there was no other choice.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And a family like our family, we had no place to go.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "You needed a lot of money.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "To Palestine, they wouldn't let you in with seven children.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And you needed a lot of money to buy those cards, just the trip alone.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And to America we couldn't go, because there was a very small quota.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We came under the Polish quota.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And the Polish quota was very small.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And again, the trip alone for us it was impossible.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 5 SECONDS]",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, it was before the war, and nobody wanted to undertake communism.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "First of all, we didn't want to be denied our religious right.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Who wanted to have their children grow up and be a communist?",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "We did not-- the feeling of the Nazi Germans yet.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "But we knew how bad the communists are.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 8 SECONDS]",
      "word_count": 4
    }
  ],
